  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2.\u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd. \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc0\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "QR Special measures to prevent possible irregularities under the code system",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Through the National Fuel Permit which will come into effect from August 1st, QR. The Information and Communication Technology Agency notes that several special measures have been taken to prevent possible abuses under the code system.",
        "QR is used to find information about people who commit such malpractices. Information and Communication Technology Agency Chairman Jayantha De Silva said that the coding system has been established.",
        "\"Even though the QR code system is in place, some members of the public have pointed out that they can get fuel by paying the fuel attendant or by some other method without showing the code.",
        "We will focus on fuel fillers under three methods. The first is direct inspection of the fuel injector and receiver. That means acting with a police officer or security personnel.",
        "Second, when a particular vehicle is refueled, we tell the owner or operator of the fuel station the amount of fuel that the vehicle has been fueled. They should bring it to scale.",
        "Third is to calculate the capacities of the fuel at the filling machine and the fuel station.",
        "Sometimes 5 liters of fuel may vary. However, if there is a difference of 30 litres, the QR will be charged at the said filling station. It is confirmed by the code or that fuel is not properly refueled.",
        "In case of such situations, the fuel station owner, manager and refuelers are responsible.",
        "QR Codes are copied by some on plastic cards and in some other ways. These can also be refueled. Or they can also refuel by showing the QR codes on their mobile phones.",
        "So far 826 fuel stations across the country have QR of National Fuel Bond. Facilities are provided for filling up under index system.",
        "We refuel under these systems for the convenience of the general public. For this, it is necessary for the general public to give their full cooperation,\" he said."
      ],
